name: Get Out The Way
description: This is the "Pink" version of my "Get Out The Way" character. The original painting was mixed media on wood. This NFT is a 1/1, which means only one of these will be minted to the blockchain. There are 3 different color versions available, but only 1 of each, so they are totally unique originals. I hope you enjoy it! Twitter: @jeffclaassen - Instagram: @jeffclaassen
